 251:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****     This subsection provides a set of functions allowing to initialize the USARTx or the UARTy
 252:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****     in asynchronous mode.
 253:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****       (+) For the asynchronous mode the parameters below can be configured:
 254:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****         (++) Baud Rate
 255:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****         (++) Word Length
 256:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****         (++) Stop Bit
 257:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****         (++) Parity: If the parity is enabled, then the MSB bit of the data written
 258:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****              in the data register is transmitted but is changed by the parity bit.
