 280:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****   8-bit or 9-bit), the possible UART formats are listed in the
 281:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****   following table.
